### ========================================
### PRUEBAS DE VALIDACIÓN DE PROPIETARIO
### ========================================

### 1. Login como HOST propietario
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "host1@test.com",
  "password": "Host123"
}

> {% client.global.set("host1_token", response.body.content.token); %}

###

### 2. Login como HOST diferente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "host2@test.com",
  "password": "Host123"
}

> {% client.global.set("host2_token", response.body.content.token); %}

###

### 3. HOST1 crea un alojamiento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{host1_token}}

{
  "title": "Casa de HOST1",
  "description": "Mi casa",
  "city": "Bogota",
  "address": "Calle 50 #10-20",
  "latitude": 4.7110,
  "longitude": -74.0721,
  "pricePerNight": 150.00,
  "maxCapacity": 5,
  "amenities": "WiFi"
}

###

### 4. ✅ HOST1 puede desactivar SU alojamiento
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{host1_token}}

###

### 5. ❌ HOST2 NO puede desactivar el alojamiento de HOST1 (debe fallar)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{host2_token}}

### Respuesta esperada:
# {
#   "error": true,
#   "content": "Solo puedes modificar el estado de tus propios alojamientos. Este alojamiento pertenece a otro anfitrión."
# }

###

### 6. ❌ HOST2 NO puede activar el alojamiento de HOST1 (debe fallar)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{host2_token}}

###

### 7. ❌ HOST2 NO puede hacer soft delete del alojamiento de HOST1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/soft
Authorization: Bearer {{host2_token}}

###

### 8. ✅ HOST1 SÍ puede hacer soft delete de SU alojamiento
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/soft
Authorization: Bearer {{host1_token}}

###